    description: "The Supreme Leader of the First Order and a master of the Knights of Ren.",
    lore: "**Ben Solo**, the son of Han Solo and Leia Organa, was once a promising student of Luke Skywalker before falling to the dark side and becoming **Kylo Ren**. Driven by a desperate, misplaced desire to finish what his grandfather, **Darth Vader**, started, he became the primary enforcer of the First Order under Supreme Leader Snoke. Wielding a unique, unstable crossguard lightsaber, he is a warrior of immense raw power but deep emotional instability.\n\nKylo's combat style is brutal and unrefined, reflecting his inner turmoil. He uses the Force as a blunt instrument, capable of freezing blaster bolts in mid-air or extracting information through painful mental probes. His journey is one of constant conflict between the 'light' and the 'dark,' a struggle that eventually led him to the throne of the First Order. Kylo Ren is a symbol of the legacy of the Skywalker family—a man of incredible potential who was nearly consumed by his own shadow before finding his way back to his true self.",
    triviaInfo: "Origin: Born Ben Solo on Chandrila, he was corrupted by Snoke at a young age. He first appeared in Star Wars: The Force Awakens (2015).\n\nBattles: He led the destruction of the New Jedi Order and was instrumental in the First Order's conquest of the galaxy. His duels with Rey are central to the sequel trilogy.\n\nSpecial Abilities & Gear: He uses a crossguard lightsaber with an unstable, cracked kyber crystal. He is exceptionally powerful in Force stasis and telepathy.\n\nSecret Trivia: Adam Driver, who played Kylo Ren, is a former U.S. Marine, which contributed to his intense and physical portrayal of the character. The unique sound of his lightsaber was created by sound designers using a combination of a toaster and a malfunctioning generator to give it its 'unstable' hum.",
