    description: "The most feared bounty hunter in the galaxy and the ruler of Tatooine's underworld.",
    lore: "**Boba Fett** is a legendary name that has struck fear into the hearts of outlaws and heroes alike for decades. An unaltered clone of the famous bounty hunter Jango Fett, he was raised to inherit his father's skills and his iconic suit of Mandalorian armor. For years, he was known as the best in the business, a cold and calculating professional who always got his mark. Following his narrow escape from the Sarlacc pit, he re-emerged with a new sense of purpose, eventually seizing the throne of Jabba the Hutt's criminal empire on Tatooine.\n\nUnlike many who rely on the Force, Boba Fett relies on his wits, his experience, and his massive arsenal of high-tech weaponry. From his jetpack-mounted missile to his wrist-mounted flamethrower, he is prepared for any situation. He values respect and loyalty above all else, ruling his territory with a code of honor that sets him apart from the selfish criminals who preceded him. Boba Fett is a survivor, a man who has looked into the mouth of death and walked away, proving that in a galaxy of gods and wizards, it is the one with the best plan and the toughest armor who ultimately survives.",
