    lore: "**R2-D2** is perhaps the most important and courageous droid in the entire galaxy. A small, dome-shaped astromech droid, he has witnessed and participated in almost every major event in galactic history, from the fall of the Republic to the rise of the First Order. Loyal, brave, and surprisingly sassy, R2 has saved the lives of heroes like Luke Skywalker, Anakin Skywalker, and Princess Leia more times than anyone can count.\n\nDespite his lack of traditional speech, R2 communicates through a series of whistles and beeps that convey a wealth of personality and intelligence. His small frame is packed with a vast array of tools, including a holoprojector, slicing tools, and even small jet-thrusters. R2-D2 is not a 'machine' in the eyes of his friends, but a constant and unwavering companion whose bravery and ingenuity have turned the tide of countless battles. He is the unsung hero of the Star Wars saga, the droid who always knows exactly what to do when everything goes wrong.",
