    description: "A survivor of Order 66 and a powerful Jedi Knight with a unique Psychometry ability.",
    lore: "**Cal Kestis** was a young Padawan when the Jedi Order fell during **Order 66**. Having survived his master Jaro Tapal's death, he spent years in hiding as a rigger on the planet Bracca, suppressing his connection to the Force to escape the Empire's Inquisitors. After being forced out of hiding, Cal began a journey of healing and rediscovery, eventually rebuilding his connection to the Force and becoming a symbol of resistance against the Empire.\n\nCal's primary gift is **Psychometry**—the rare ability to sense the history and emotions attached to an object or location. In combat, he uses a specialized modular lightsaber that can transform into both double-bladed and dual-wielded forms. Always at his side is **BD-1**, a small astromech droid who provides him with tactical information and medical aid. Cal's journey of growth and his willingness to face his propria trauma have made him one of the galaxy's most resilient and determined Jedi. He is a 'survivor' in every sense of the word, a warrior who refuses to let the light of the Jedi fade into history.",
